title: United Kingdom Imports of Live Animals
description: Imports of Live Animals in the United Kingdom decreased to 52.70 GBP Million in September from 59.63 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Live Animals in the United Kingdom averaged 37.07 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 172.14 GBP Million in October of 2019 and a record low of 1.96 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Live Animals.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
